plot: On a cross-shaped island in the South, a mysterious and gigantic humanoid robot known as the &"Cybuddy&" is discovered sealed in the underground ruins for untold ages. A group known as the &"Order of the Glittering Star Cross&" attempts to remove the seal by abducting a girl named Wako Agemaki, who they dubbed the &"shrine maiden&" and is the key to activating the robot. A boy named Takuto Tsunashi arrives with his own Cybuddy named Tauburn to rescue Wako. Thus begins a struggle to unlock the secrets of the advanced technology and prevent disaster.   Written by  ANN
title: Star Driver Kagayaki no Takuto
